{"type":"message","id":"fd0b7def","parentId":"1998c0be","timestamp":"2026-03-10T00:53:45.692Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_MM1gNudjICXXyfjtzINSuVD0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Changelog\n\nAll notable changes to the `long-prompt-orchestrator` skill will be documented in this file.\n\nThe format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),\nand this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).\n\n## [Unreleased]\n\n### Planned\n- Dynamic replanning based on execution results\n- Improved resource estimation models\n- Enhanced skill recommendation algorithms\n- Checkpoint and recovery mechanisms\n\n## [1.0.0] - 2026-03-09\n\n### Added\n- **Complete documentation suite**:\n  - `MAIN_AGENT_INTEGRATION_GUIDE.md` - Comprehensive main agent integration guide\n  - `PLAN_FORMAT_SPECIFICATION.md` - Complete JSON schema specification\n  - `LONG_PROMPT_ORCHESTRATOR_CORRECTED_ARCHITECTURE.md` - Architecture documentation\n  - `VALIDATION_REPORT.md` - Validation results and recommendations\n  - `FINAL_SUMMARY.md` - Executive summary and status report\n  - `QUICK_START_GUIDE.md` - Quick start guide for main agents\n  - `CHANGELOG.md` - This changelog file\n\n- **Integration prototypes**:\n  - `scripts/plan_executor_prototype.py` - Plan executor prototype for main agents\n  - Enhanced examples in `examples/` directory\n\n[168 more lines in file. Use offset=31 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773104025679}}
{"type":"message","id":"4d288480","parentId":"fd0b7def","timestamp":"2026-03-10T00:53:58.571Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Let me add an entry to the CHANGELOG about this fix:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_czffefDEzr5HGoOk6uRS0xz4","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/long-prompt-orchestrator/CHANGELOG.md","oldText":"## [Unreleased]\n\n### Planned\n- Dynamic replanning based on execution results\n- Improved resource estimation models\n- Enhanced skill recommendation algorithms\n- Checkpoint and recovery mechanisms","newText":"## [Unreleased]\n\n### Fixed\n- **Critical bug fix**: Skill recommendation logic no longer incorrectly recommends `salesforce-code-auditor` for non-Salesforce tasks\n  - Issue: Tasks like \"Inventory workspace skills and check system health\" were incorrectly matched to `salesforce-code-auditor`\n  - Fix: Updated `_recommend_skill_or_role()` in `plan_generator.py` and `_analyze_skill_recommendation()` in `distributed_orchestrate.py`\n  - Now correctly recommends: `workspace-janitor` for workspace tasks, `agent-watchdog` for system health, etc.\n  - Salesforce tasks still correctly map to Salesforce skills\n  - Enables real delegation testing with proper skill matching\n\n### Planned\n- Dynamic replanning based on execution results\n- Improved resource estimation models\n- Enhanced skill recommendation algorithms\n- Checkpoint and recovery mechanisms"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":383,"output":338,"cacheRead":45824,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46545,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773104025691}}
